    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Padded hoods used inside the helmet for jousting, so as to hold the wearer's head firmly in place against the shock and whiplash of being struck with a lance.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
